== My Favourite Bangla Blogs

This is basically an RSS reader, with added functionality that it checks for blog update several times a day.
It also crawl the blog post pages to get the comment count, ratings etc. which are not available in RSS feed.

=== How to use

First of all, you need openid account to login.
Just log in, it will bring you to the blog listing page. You can add/edit your blog selection.
Go to Posts page (not implemented yet) to view the update

If many user starts using it, then it can have association analysis. Association mining will make this software suggest others the blog he/she might find interesting
